➜连江的海之角，我在平流尾等你
http://www.sohu.com/a/430914127_125202	39471
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201110/da3cf51d3cc5484fb08a9c02d0f41651.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201110/f7b46e357a81483e92b3aff3f3047f98.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人类</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多少的梦想寄托于大海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们的征途</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是星辰也是海洋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201110/340c13109c974e27bc14753abf3e703c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
